data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET!! BUYER COULD NOT PERFORM!! Welcome to this fully remodeled 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home in a serene and quiet neighborhood. Meticulously updated, this residence radiates modern elegance without sacrificing comfort. The open-concept living space features a newly renovated kitchen with contemporary fixtures, sleek countertops, and stainless steel appliances. The master bedroom includes an ensuite bathroom, providing a private retreat. The two additional bedrooms share a tastefully redesigned bathroom. Throughout the home, discover fresh paint, new flooring, and modern fixtures that contribute to its stylish ambiance. Step outside to the large fenced backyard, offering a perfect retreat for outdoor activities or simply unwinding in a peaceful setting. This home combines thoughtful design and tranquility, creating a welcoming haven in a sought-after neighborhood.
